title: Munchkin
description: Munchkin is a simple, card-based game chock full o' silliness.

title: Munchkin: Deluxe
description: Munchkin is a simple, card-based game chock full o' silliness. Deluxe set includes standies and a gameboard.

title: Munchkin: Disney
description: Fight Disney villains and collect Treasure to Level Up as you become the top Disney fan around

title: Munchkin: Marvel
description: 168 cards feature iconic characters from the Marvel universe

title: Munchkin: Rick and Morty
description: Must have edition for Munchkin fans and collectors, perfect for Rick and Morty or Munchkin fans alike

title: Munchkin: Critical Role
description: Fight familiar Critical Role Mighty Nein adversaries and collect Treasure to Level Up

title: Munchkin: Harry Potter
description: Get ready for an epic duel in this collectible Munchkin game featuring artwork, characters, and spells from the Harry Potter movies where you race to prove your mettle against other witches and wizards.

title: Munchkin: Apocalypse
description: It's the end of the world! In Munchkin: Apocolypse, every possible natural (and unnatural) disaster has happened... or is about to. You are a rugged survivor in a world full of people - and things - that want to kill you and take your stuff. So do it to them first.

title: Munchkin: Harry Potter Deluxe
description: Play as a member of your favorite Hogwarts house - Gryffindor, Slytherin, Hufflepuff, and Ravenclaw. Defeat villains and monsters all while outwitting the other players - but watch out for wandering monsters to derail your progress.

title: Star Munchkin: Deluxe
description: Kill the monsters. Steal the treasure. Stab your buddy... in space!

title: Munchkin: X-Men
description: Perfect gift for Marvel comic book fans!

title: Munchkin: Dungeon
description: Push Your Luck - Players can travel through as many dungeon rooms on their turn as they want, but the further they go, the tougher the fight at the end.

title: Munchkin: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
description: Officially licensed game based on the fan-favorite comic book series and Munchkin card game

title: Munchkin: Crazy Cooks
description: Play this alone or combine it with any other Munchkin games! This Deluxe edition comes with 168 cards, food tokens, a gameboard, and a custom 6-sided die!

title: Munchkin: Pathfinder
description: Get the fast and fun gameplay of Munchkin with the fantasy flavor of Pathfinder in one neat package!
